name: Eden °_°
description:
We know that we do not take care of the garden.
We know we should be more cautious.
We know that we have been unfair to very many people.
We know we should be helpful and less selfish.
We know we should have a strong work ethic and integrity.
There are people who fail to evaluate the meaning of repentance in terms of deeds, as though it were an exercise in moralistic gymnastics.
